\c 24
\s Ukubusa kukaJowashi koJuda
\p
\v 1 UJowashi wayeleminyaka eyisikhombisa esiba yinkosi, wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amane eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguZibiya weBherishebha\x + 1 Kho. 12.1-15.\x*.
\v 2 UJowashi wasesenza okuqondileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 26.5.\x*\nd* insuku zonke zikaJehoyada umpristi\x + 24.14,17-22.\x*.
\v 3 UJehoyada wasemthathela abafazi ababili; wasezala amadodana lamadodakazi\x + Gen. 5.4.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokho kwaba senhliziyweni kaJowashi ukuvuselela indlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 29.10. 1 Lan. 22.7.\x*\nd*.
\v 5 Wasebuthanisa abapristi lamaLevi, wathi kibo: Phumani liye emizini yakoJuda, liqoqe kuIsrayeli wonke imali yokulungisa indlu kaNkulunkulu wenu umnyaka ngomnyaka; lina-ke, luphangiseleni udaba\x + 21.2.\x*. Kodwa amaLevi kawaphangisanga\x + 2 Kho. 12.6,7.\x*.
\v 6 Inkosi yasibiza uJehoyada inhloko, yathi kuye: Kungani ungabizanga kumaLevi ukuthi alethe esusa koJuda laseJerusalema umthelo kaMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 30.12-16. 2 Kho. 12.4.\x*\nd*, lowebandla lakoIsrayeli okwethente lobufakazi\x + Nani 17.7.\x*?
\v 7 Ngoba amadodana kaAthaliya okhohlakeleyo afohlela endlini kaNkulunkulu\x + 21.17.\x*, futhi-ke ayesebenzisele oBhali zonke izinto ezingcwele zendlu yeN\nd kosi\x + 1 Kho. 15.15.\x*\nd*.
\v 8 Inkosi yasilaya, asesenza ibhokisi elilodwa, alibeka esangweni lendlu kaJehova phandle\x + 2 Kho. 12.9.\x*.
\v 9 Asesenza isimemezelo koJuda laseJerusalema ukuthi balethe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni umthelo kaMozisi inceku kaNkulunkulu \add owabekwa\add* phezu kukaIsrayeli enkangala\x + 24.6.\x*.
\v 10 Zonke iziphathamandla labo bonke abantu basebethokoza, baletha baphosela ebhokisini baze baqeda.
\v 11 Kwakusithi-ke ngesikhathi eletha ibhokisi kumhloli wenkosi ngesandla samaLevi, lalapho ebona ukuthi kulemali enengi, umabhalane wenkosi lenduna yompristi oyinhloko beze balithulule ibhokisi, balithathe balibuyisele endaweni yalo. Benza njalo-ke insuku ngensuku, baqoqa imali ngobunengi.
\v 12 Inkosi loJehoyada basebeyinika abenzi bomsebenzi wenkonzo wendlu kaJehova, baqatsha abakha ngamatshe lababazi ukuvuselela indlu kaJehova, njalo labakhandi bensimbi lethusi ukuqinisa indlu kaJehova\x + 24.5.\x*.
\v 13 Ngakho abenzi bomsebenzi basebenza, kwaze kwathi ukuvuselelwa komsebenzi kwaqhubeka ngesandla sabo, bayimisa indlu kaNkulunkulu ngesilinganiso sayo, bayiqinisa.
\v 14 Kwathi sebeqedile baletha imali eseleyo phambi kwenkosi loJehoyada, abenza ngayo izitsha zendlu kaJehova, izitsha zenkonzo lezokunikela, lezinkezo, lezitsha zegolide lezesiliva\x + 2 Kho. 12.13.\x*. Basebenikela njalonjalo iminikelo yokutshiswa endlini kaJehova zonke izinsuku zikaJehoyada\x + 24.2.\x*.
\p
\v 15 UJehoyada waseguga wenela ngezinsuku, wafa; wayeleminyaka elikhulu lamatshumi amathathu ekufeni kwakhe\x + 1 Lan. 23.1.\x*.
\v 16 Basebemngcwabela emzini kaDavida lamakhosi, ngoba wayenze okulungileyo koIsrayeli lakuNkulunkulu lendlu yakhe\x + 21.2.\x*.
\v 17 Emva kokufa kukaJehoyada iziphathamandla zakoJuda zasezisiza zakhothama phambi kwenkosi; khona inkosi yazilalela.
\v 18 Basebeyitshiya indlu yeN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, bakhonza izixuku\x + 1 Kho. 14.23. Eks. 34.13.\x* lezithombe\x + 1 Sam. 31.9. 2 Sam. 5.21.\x*. Kwasekusehlela ulaka phezu kukaJuda leJerusalema ngenxa yalelicala labo\x + 19.2,10. 29.8. 32.25. 28.11,13.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa yathuma abaprofethi phakathi kwabo ukubabuyisela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 36.15.\x*; basebefakaza bemelene labo, kodwa kababekanga indlebe\x + Neh. 13.15,21.\x*.
\v 20 UMoya kaNkulunkulu wasesembesa uZekhariya indodana kaJehoyada umpristi owema ngaphezu kwabantu, wathi kibo: Utsho njalo uNkulunkulu: Kungani liseqa imilayo yeN\nd kosi\nd* ukuze lingaphumeleli\x + Nani 14.41.\x*? Ngoba liyitshiyile iN\nd kosi\nd*, layo ilitshiyile\x + 24.24. 15.2.\x*.
\v 21 Basebemenzela ugobe, bamkhanda ngamatshe ngomlayo wenkosi\x + Neh. 9.26.\x*, egumeni lendlu kaJehova\x + Mat. 23.35. Luka 11.51.\x*.
\v 22 Ngokunjalo uJowashi inkosi kawukhumbulanga umusa uJehoyada uyise ayemenzele wona, kodwa wabulala indodana yakhe\x + Josh. 2.14.\x*. Lalapho esifa wathi: IN\nd kosi\nd* kayibone\x + 1 Sam. 24.15.\x* i\add ku\add*fune\x + Gen. 9.5.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Kwasekusithi ekuthwaseni komnyaka ibutho leSiriya lenyuka lamelana laye\x + 2 Kho. 12.17,18.\x*; basebefika koJuda leJerusalema, babhubhisa zonke iziphathamandla zabantu ebantwini, bathumela yonke impango yazo enkosini yeDamaseko\x + 24.17.\x*.
\v 24 Lanxa ibutho lamaSiriya leza lilamadoda amalutshwana, kanti iN\nd kosi\nd* yanikela esandleni sawo ibutho elikhulu kakhulu, ngoba babeyitshiyile iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu waboyise\x + Isa. 30.17. Levi 26.36,37.\x*. Ngalokho benza izigwebo kuJowashi\x + 22.8. Isa. 10.5.\x*.
\v 25 Kwathi sebesukile kuye, ngoba bemtshiye esemikhuhlaneni emikhulu\x + Dute. 28.35.\x*, inceku zakhe zamenzela ugobe\x + 24.27,2 Kho. 12.20,21.\x* ngenxa yegazi lamadodana kaJehoyada umpristi, zambulalela embhedeni wakhe, wasesifa; basebemngcwabela emzini kaDavida\x + 24.21,22.\x*, kodwa kabamngcwabanga emangcwabeni amakhosi\x + 21.20. 28.27. 2 Kho. 12.21.\x*.
\v 26 Lalaba yibo ababemenzele ugobe: OZabadi indodana kaShimeyathi umAmonikazi, loJehozabadi indodana kaShimirithi umMowabikazi.
\p
\v 27 Mayelana lamadodana akhe, lobukhulu bomthwalo phezu kwakhe, lokumiswa kwendlu kaNkulunkulu, khangela, kubhaliwe endabeni yogwalo lwamakhosi. UAmaziya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + 24.11,12.\x*.
